This package contains the Ochi source package -- a part of HAvOc.

See the file INSTALL for generic compilation and installation instructions.

See the section FAQ in the documentation (doc/faq.txt) for
frequently asked questions.  

Compilation of the source requires leptonica and zbar.  More on installation and
compilation in INSTALLATION.

Please send bug reports to <samo.penic@fe.uni-lj.si>.  Please include the
version number, and a complete, self-contained test case in each bug report.

If you have questions about using Ochi and the documentation does
not answer them, please send mail to <samo.penc@fe.uni-lj.si>.


Translations:
For translations GNU project gettext should be used.
brief procedure:
xgettext -d ochi -s -o ochi.pot main.c
msginit -l sl_SI -o slovenian.po -i ochi.pot
(edit file slovenian.po)
msgfmt -c -v -o ochi.mo slovenian.po

Then set locale: export LC_ALL=sl_SI.utf8
and run the program.
